12:28.916 --> 12:30.984
DON'T ‐‐ COME ON.
GOD.

12:34.388 --> 12:35.155
AHH.

12:35.189 --> 12:39.426
SO, TELL ME,
WHO IS THIS...CLIENT?

12:39.459 --> 12:42.129
I CAN'T DIVULGE
PRIVILEGED INFORMATION.

12:42.162 --> 12:44.331
BUT IT RHYMES WITH "DRUG"
AND "HILAS."

12:44.364 --> 12:46.500
THEIR "POP" CLUB
GOT "RUSTED,"

12:46.533 --> 12:49.203
AND THEY NEED TO GET
THEIR "SHMARIJUANA"

12:49.236 --> 12:50.804
BACK FROM THE "GROLICE."

12:50.838 --> 12:51.939
OF COURSE.

12:51.972 --> 12:54.007
THEY HAVE A ROOMFUL
OF "SHMARIJUANA,"

12:54.041 --> 12:56.443
AND I HAVE A ROOMFUL
OF YOU'RE PRETTY!

12:56.476 --> 12:57.911
I'M SO FUCKED.

12:57.945 --> 13:01.315
I SELL A PRODUCT
THAT NOBODY WANTS.

13:01.348 --> 13:04.051
AND YOU...

13:04.084 --> 13:06.887
YOU HAVE ALL OF THIS POT

13:06.920 --> 13:11.391
THAT BELONGS
TO FUCKING ASSHOLES.

13:11.425 --> 13:14.461
HILAS ISN'T AN ASSHOLE.
HE'S A NICE KID.

13:14.494 --> 13:16.663
OH, REALLY?
HE IS?

13:16.697 --> 13:17.998
[ POT THUDS ]

13:18.031 --> 13:19.967
WHAT DID SILAS PAY YOU

13:20.000 --> 13:22.736
FOR ALL OF YOUR VALUABLE
LEGAL ADVICE, DEAN?

13:22.769 --> 13:23.904
I'M SMOKIN' IT.

13:23.937 --> 13:25.138
TELL ME SOMETHING ‐‐

13:25.172 --> 13:28.909
ARE YOU A CLOSER,
OR ARE YOU A LOSER?

13:28.942 --> 13:30.544
I LIKE TO CLOSE DRAWERS.

13:30.577 --> 13:31.478
[ DRAWER SLAMS ]

13:31.512 --> 13:33.580
ALL RIGHT,
WELL, CLOSE THE DRAWER, THEN,

13:33.614 --> 13:35.349
AND OPEN YOUR MIND.

13:35.382 --> 13:39.319
I COULD SELL
A LOT MORE MAKEUP

13:39.353 --> 13:42.756
IF I GIVE A FREE GIFT
WITH PURCHASE.

13:42.789 --> 13:44.258
OH, NO.

13:44.291 --> 13:46.326
I‐I‐I‐I‐I CAN'T STEAL
THEIR WEED.

13:46.360 --> 13:49.897
JUST TELL THEM THAT YOU GOT
RIPPED OFF BY BLACK PEOPLE.

13:49.930 --> 13:50.964
THEY WON'T BUY THAT.

13:50.998 --> 13:52.833
THEY WILL
WHEN THEY SEE THE BRUISES.

13:52.866 --> 13:54.401
WHAT BRUISES?

13:54.434 --> 13:55.769
OHH!

13:55.802 --> 13:57.571
OW!

13:57.604 --> 13:59.006
PUTZ.

13:59.039 --> 14:02.409
YOU KNOW, I ADMIRE YOU.

14:02.442 --> 14:03.777
GO AWAY.

14:03.810 --> 14:05.045
THIS IS MY SPOT.

14:05.078 --> 14:07.915
DESPITE THE BACKWARDS NATURE
OF YOUR CONVICTIONS,

14:07.948 --> 14:09.249
YOU'RE TENACIOUS.

14:09.283 --> 14:11.485
AND THAT BESPEAKS A CERTAIN
SOMETHING OF SOMETHING,

14:11.518 --> 14:12.786
SO BRAVO.

14:12.819 --> 14:14.388
HEY, WAIT.
WHAT SIDE ARE YOU ON?

14:14.421 --> 14:16.790
I'M ON THE SIDE
OF STICKING TO ONE'S GUNS!

14:16.823 --> 14:18.525
I FINALLY SAID NO TO HER.

14:18.559 --> 14:22.429
OH, GOD, THE WAVE OF RELIEF
THAT WASHED OVER ME,

14:22.462 --> 14:23.797
WEIRD PROTESTER GUY.

14:23.830 --> 14:25.299
I'M BUOYANT.

14:25.332 --> 14:26.967
I'M A BUOY.

14:27.000 --> 14:29.570
AHH!
BLUEBIRDS ON MY SHOULDERS.

14:29.603 --> 14:30.637
ANDY?

14:30.671 --> 14:32.873
HOW'S NANCY?
IS THE BABY OKAY?

14:32.906 --> 14:33.907
BABY MURDERER!

14:33.941 --> 14:35.509
25 FEET, GAYLE.

14:35.542 --> 14:36.944
BABY'S FINE.

14:36.977 --> 14:40.781
1,000 SUNS
IN THOSE CHUBBY CHEEKS.

14:40.814 --> 14:42.216
YOU'RE WEARING ARMOR.

14:42.249 --> 14:44.418
WELL, YOU CAN NEVER BE
TOO CAREFUL.

14:44.451 --> 14:45.319
AND YOU'RE SMOKING.

14:45.352 --> 14:47.821
SOMETIMES YOU CAN BE
TOO CAREFUL.

14:47.855 --> 14:49.756
CAN I HELP YOU
WITH SOMETHING?

14:49.790 --> 14:51.758
I, UH...

14:51.792 --> 14:52.860
YOU WANT TO GO OUT?

14:52.893 --> 14:54.595
I'LL BUY YOU DINNER.
I SHAVED.

14:54.628 --> 14:55.863
WHEN?

14:55.896 --> 14:57.331
JUST NOW.
JUST RIGHT BEFORE I CAME.

14:57.364 --> 14:59.299
NO.
WHEN DO YOU WANT TO GO OUT?

14:59.333 --> 15:00.701
OH.

15:00.734 --> 15:01.902
TONIGHT.

15:01.935 --> 15:04.104
PICK ME UP HERE AT 7:00.

15:04.137 --> 15:06.306
HOW WILL I KNOW YOUR CAR?

15:06.340 --> 15:08.175
IT HAS
A DISTINCTIVE HORN.

15:08.208 --> 15:10.944
YOU'RE IN THE CROSS HAIRS
OF THE RIGHTEOUS!

15:10.978 --> 15:13.780
IGNORE THE DARK WARNINGS
AT YOUR OWN PERIL!

15:13.814 --> 15:14.948
TAKE A CLARITIN, GAYLE.

15:14.982 --> 15:16.984
TODAY'S POLLEN COUNT
IS OFF THE CHARTS.

15:17.017 --> 15:18.085
I'LL GET THAT.

15:18.118 --> 15:19.820
I'LL SEE YOU AT 7:00.

15:19.853 --> 15:21.054
YES.

15:22.856 --> 15:24.491
SHE LIKES ME.

15:24.525 --> 15:26.627
SHE'S GONNA BURN IN HELL
FOR ALL OF ETERNITY.

15:26.660 --> 15:30.564
WELL, I'D RATHER LAUGH
WITH THE SINNERS, GAYLE.

15:30.597 --> 15:32.733
FOR NOW.

15:35.936 --> 15:38.372
[ DOG BARKING, SNARLING ]

15:42.976 --> 15:45.312
Lupita.
THANK YOU.

15:45.345 --> 15:46.213
GOOD TIMING.

15:46.246 --> 15:48.282
WILLIAM MORRIS
JUST MERGED WITH ENDEAVOR.

15:48.315 --> 15:50.517
AND MR. KAPLAN ‐‐
OUT ON HIS ASS.

15:53.887 --> 15:55.856
LOOK LIKE A DIVE BAR.

15:55.889 --> 15:58.192
YEAH, I HAVEN'T HAD TIME
TO REDECORATE.

15:58.225 --> 15:59.927
SO, WHERE'S MY BEDROOM?

15:59.960 --> 16:02.029
WE'RE A LITTLE SHORT
ON BEDROOMS.

16:02.996 --> 16:05.465
UH, UPSTAIRS. UPSTAIRS.

16:05.499 --> 16:07.734
YOUR BEDROOM'S UPSTAIRS.
I'M SLEEPING ON THE COUCH.

16:07.768 --> 16:10.804
I HAD MY LAST BABY
WHEN I WAS 52.

16:10.838 --> 16:13.807
THE WOMEN IN MY FAMILY
BLEED FOREVER.

16:13.841 --> 16:14.842
WOW.

16:14.875 --> 16:16.443
HOW OLD ARE YOU?
37.

16:16.476 --> 16:19.746
SO, THE BABY ‐‐
ONE‐NIGHT STAND?

16:19.780 --> 16:21.715
A LITTLE MORE COMPLICATED
THAN THAT.

16:21.748 --> 16:22.950
MAYBE HE LEAVE HIS WIFE.

16:22.983 --> 16:24.551
EVEN MORE COMPLICATED.

16:24.585 --> 16:26.920
GOOD TO SEE YOU, NANCY.

16:26.954 --> 16:28.856
YOU PAY ME CASH.
YOU FEED ME.

16:28.889 --> 16:30.824
I NO WORK ON SUNDAYS

16:30.858 --> 16:32.960
OR WHEN "SECRETOS HOUSTON"
IS ON TV.

16:32.993 --> 16:34.895
DONE.
NO CLEANING.
NO LAUNDRY.

16:34.928 --> 16:36.597
JUST BABY.

16:36.630 --> 16:38.498
DONE.

16:38.532 --> 16:39.833
I LIKE IT.

16:39.867 --> 16:41.368
THIS IS NICE.

16:41.401 --> 16:42.169
OCEAN.

16:42.202 --> 16:44.404
MAYBE I START SURFING AGAIN.

16:44.438 --> 16:45.806
[ GASPS ]

16:45.839 --> 16:47.908
DIOS MIO, SHANE!

16:47.941 --> 16:48.909
SO TALL!

16:48.942 --> 16:50.077
HI, LUPITA.

16:50.110 --> 16:51.778
YOU SURF, TOO?
NO.

16:51.812 --> 16:53.113
I TEACH YOU.
OKAY.

16:53.146 --> 16:54.781
SURFING LESSONS EXTRA.

16:54.815 --> 16:56.083
OF COURSE THEY ARE.

16:56.116 --> 16:58.585
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:58.619 --> 16:59.786
OH!

16:59.820 --> 17:01.955
UM, OREGON?

17:01.989 --> 17:03.023
YEAH.

17:03.056 --> 17:04.458
AND THEN WEST GERMANY.

17:04.491 --> 17:05.459
MM‐HMM.

17:05.492 --> 17:07.160
AND THEN URUGUAY.

17:07.194 --> 17:07.961
YOU?

17:07.995 --> 17:09.863
TARZANA.

17:09.897 --> 17:13.467
AND THEN THE OTHER SIDE
OF TARZANA.

17:13.500 --> 17:14.468
HMM.

17:14.501 --> 17:16.803
WHAT DID YOU WANT TO BE
WHEN YOU WERE A KID?

17:16.837 --> 17:18.906
JANE GOODALL.
YOU?

17:18.939 --> 17:20.240
A DOG.

17:20.274 --> 17:23.577
THIS IS FUN.
I'M HAVING FUN.

17:26.313 --> 17:28.882
UM...IT'S GETTING
KIND OF LATE.

17:28.916 --> 17:30.851
I THINK I SHOULD GO SOON.

17:30.884 --> 17:32.052
WHAT?

17:32.085 --> 17:34.788
HAVEN'T EVEN GOTTEN
OUR COMBO PLATOS YET.

17:34.821 --> 17:35.856
ARE YOU FEELING OKAY?

17:35.889 --> 17:36.990
YEAH,
I'M ‐‐ I'M GREAT.

17:37.024 --> 17:38.825
I, UH ‐‐ JUST CONSIDERING
MY OPTIONS

17:38.859 --> 17:40.227
FOR THE REST
OF THE EVENING.

17:40.260 --> 17:42.696
AND RIGHT NOW MY PJ's AND THE
"FRIDAY NIGHT LIGHTS" BOX SET

17:42.729 --> 17:43.797
IS WINNING HANDS DOWN.

17:43.830 --> 17:45.165
[ LAUGHS ]

17:48.268 --> 17:50.437
WE'RE HAVING A GREAT DATE.
WHAT'S WRONG?

17:50.470 --> 17:51.371
NUTSHELL?

17:51.405 --> 17:52.840
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
I'M PAST YOU.

17:52.873 --> 17:54.575
PAST ME IN WHAT?
IN LIFE.

17:54.608 --> 17:57.945
LOOK, ANDY, I KNOW
THERE ARE PLENTY OF GIRLS

17:57.978 --> 18:00.581
THAT WOULD BE DAZZLED
BY $2 TACO NIGHT AT BORRACHO'S

18:00.614 --> 18:03.150
AND THE FACT THAT YOU
CAN BALANCE THE SALTSHAKER

18:03.183 --> 18:04.585
ON THE BRIDGE OF YOUR NOSE.

18:04.618 --> 18:07.855
BUT, HONESTLY, YOU LOST ME
ABOUT 15 MINUTES IN.

18:07.888 --> 18:09.523
THIS IS STUNNING.

18:09.556 --> 18:10.791
I'M STUNNED.

18:10.824 --> 18:12.392
STUNNED? REALLY?

18:12.426 --> 18:13.660
YOU'RE UNEMPLOYED.

18:13.694 --> 18:15.696
YOU'RE CLOSER TO 40
THAN 30.

18:15.729 --> 18:17.898
YOU DRIVE A CAR
FROM A TV SHOW.

18:17.931 --> 18:19.633
AND YOUR GREATEST
RECENT ACCOMPLISHMENT

18:19.666 --> 18:22.469
WAS BEATING THE UPSIDE‐DOWN
KILL SCREEN IN MS. PAC‐MAN.

18:22.503 --> 18:25.038
I DIDN'T BEAT IT.
I JUST GOT TO IT.

18:25.072 --> 18:26.840
DIED ALMOST IMMEDIATELY.

18:26.874 --> 18:28.775
THE THING'S UPSIDE DOWN.

18:28.809 --> 18:30.477
YOU'RE A FROZEN MARGARITA,
ANDY.

18:30.511 --> 18:32.746
WELL, I HAPPEN TO LIKE
SLUSHY BEVERAGES, YOU KNOW?

18:32.779 --> 18:34.548
AND I'M A DOCTOR.

18:34.581 --> 18:36.283
WOW.

18:36.316 --> 18:37.851
OKAY.

18:37.885 --> 18:40.754
FINE.
YOU'RE A DOCTOR.

18:40.787 --> 18:42.656
I PLAY DOCTOR.

18:44.424 --> 18:46.660
[ SIGHS ]

18:46.693 --> 18:49.396
UM, WHY DID YOU EVEN AGREE
TO GO OUT WITH ME?

18:49.429 --> 18:52.332
'CAUSE MY MOTHER ALWAYS SAID
THAT, "IF THEY FEED YOU, GO."

18:52.366 --> 18:53.901
BUT I'M STARTING
TO REALIZE

18:53.934 --> 18:55.869
MY MOTHER GAVE ME
LOTS OF BAD ADVICE.

18:55.903 --> 18:58.405
THANK YOU FOR THE DRINK.

18:58.438 --> 19:00.440
WELL, UH...

19:00.474 --> 19:01.742
I‐I'LL DRIVE YOU HOME.

19:01.775 --> 19:02.843
NO, IT'S ALL RIGHT.

19:02.876 --> 19:04.044
I'LL FIND MY OWN WAY,

19:04.077 --> 19:06.780
PREFERABLY IN A CAR
WHERE THE DOORS OPEN.

19:06.813 --> 19:08.081
GOOD NIGHT, ANDY.

19:19.826 --> 19:21.595
THIS BABY SLEEP TOO MUCH.

19:21.628 --> 19:25.599
IT PROBABLY JUST WANTS
TO WAKE UP WHEN IT'S ALL OVER.

19:25.632 --> 19:26.834
OH, SHIT.

19:26.867 --> 19:28.602
NOW I'M CALLING IT
AN "IT."

19:28.635 --> 19:31.205
"HIM" AN "IT."
"HIM" A "HIM."

19:31.238 --> 19:33.607
I NEED TO NAME THIS BABY.

19:33.640 --> 19:35.309
I GO SURF NOW.

19:35.342 --> 19:38.745
I LIKE BERNARDO,
LIKE IN "WEST SIDE STORY."

19:38.779 --> 19:41.815
BERNARDO BOTWIN.

19:41.849 --> 19:42.850
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

19:42.883 --> 19:45.419
BERNARDO?
HE GETS KILLED BY TONY.

19:45.452 --> 19:49.089
IF YOU SIGN THE BIRTH
CERTIFICATE, HE'D BE ANDY JR.

19:49.122 --> 19:51.458
THAT'S WHAT I CALL
MY PENIS.

19:51.491 --> 19:52.926
WAIT, NO, GOD!

19:52.960 --> 19:54.795
I NEED TO STOP PLAYING DOCTOR
AND BE A DOCTOR.

19:54.828 --> 19:55.796
WHAT?

19:55.829 --> 19:56.964
UGH.

19:56.997 --> 19:58.599
I WANT TO DO THIS.
I WANT TO BE THE FATHER.

19:58.632 --> 19:59.766
REALLY?!
REALLY.

19:59.800 --> 20:02.135
YAY!
BUT I MEAN REALLY,
REALLY.

20:02.169 --> 20:04.538
IF MY NAME IS ON THIS CHILD'S
BIRTH CERTIFICATE,

20:04.571 --> 20:05.772
THEN I WILL BE ITS FATHER.

20:05.806 --> 20:07.274
AND WE WILL RAISE IT
TOGETHER.

20:07.307 --> 20:08.208
HIM.
HIM.

20:08.242 --> 20:10.344
50% OWNERSHIP.
HALF THE VOTING SHARES.

20:10.377 --> 20:12.746
AND I'M ON THE BIMAH
AT THE BAR MITZVAH.

20:12.779 --> 20:14.414
OH, HE'S JEWISH NOW?

20:14.448 --> 20:15.516
REFORM, BUT YEAH.

20:15.549 --> 20:17.751
AND JUST SO YOU KNOW,
I'M NOT DOING THIS FOR YOU.

20:17.784 --> 20:19.853
THIS IS FOR ME.

20:19.887 --> 20:21.822
I WANT SOMETHING THAT MATTERS
IN MY LIFE.

20:21.855 --> 20:23.891
I WANT TO BE
A SUBSTANTIAL HUMAN BEING.

20:23.924 --> 20:26.793
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
SUBSTANTIAL.

20:26.827 --> 20:27.895
YEAH.

20:27.928 --> 20:29.763
SUBSTANTIAL.

20:29.796 --> 20:31.298
[ BABY CRYING ]

20:31.331 --> 20:34.902
OOH,
HE'S SUBSTANTIALLY WET.

20:34.935 --> 20:37.304
I THINK YOU SHOULD CHANGE HIM,
PAPA.

20:37.337 --> 20:39.806
UH...

20:39.840 --> 20:41.875
ALL RIGHT.

20:41.909 --> 20:43.744
WHAT'S UP?

20:43.777 --> 20:46.046
ALL RIGHT, COME ON,
LITTLE BUDDY.

20:46.079 --> 20:48.815
LET'S SEE WHAT YOU'RE PACKING
DOWNSTAIRS.

20:48.849 --> 20:49.883
MM‐HMM.

20:49.917 --> 20:53.787
LET'S SEE WHAT'S GOING ON
DOWN HERE.

20:53.820 --> 20:55.656
I KNOW IT.

20:55.689 --> 20:56.790
WHOA!

20:56.823 --> 20:58.292
BUN'S STILL
ON THE HOT DOG.

20:58.325 --> 21:00.794
OH, RIGHT, THAT.
I GOT TO TAKE CARE OF THAT.

21:00.827 --> 21:01.895
NEXT CHECKUP.

21:01.929 --> 21:03.363
CHECKUP?
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

21:03.397 --> 21:05.599
A BRISS
WITH A MOHEL AND A RABBI.

21:05.632 --> 21:06.700
[ CRYING INTENSIFIES ]

21:06.733 --> 21:09.570
YEAH, BAGELS AND WHITEFISH.
THOSE ARE MY DEMANDS.

21:09.603 --> 21:10.904
DEMANDS?

21:10.938 --> 21:13.607
THAT'S RIGHT.
'CAUSE I'M THE PAPA.

21:13.640 --> 21:15.142
I'M THE PAPA.

21:15.175 --> 21:15.943
YES.

21:15.976 --> 21:17.578
TRADITION.

21:17.611 --> 21:18.579
OY.

21:18.612 --> 21:20.480
[ BABY CRYING ]

21:20.514 --> 21:21.615
OHH.

21:29.923 --> 21:31.558
WHO ARE ALL THESE PEOPLE?

21:31.592 --> 21:32.893
THE RABBI BROUGHT THEM.

21:32.926 --> 21:34.728
APPARENTLY,
YOU NEED 10 JEWS

21:34.761 --> 21:37.664
TO WATCH HIM LOSE HIS DICK HEAD
OR IT'S NOT OFFICIAL.

21:38.866 --> 21:39.833
[ SNIPS ]

21:39.867 --> 21:41.001
OHH.

21:41.034 --> 21:42.135
[ CROWD OHHs ]

21:42.169 --> 21:43.704
[ CRYING INTENSIFIES ]

21:43.737 --> 21:45.839
THAT'S IT.
MAZEL TOV.

21:45.873 --> 21:49.009
LET'S NAME THIS BABY
AND EAT.

21:51.044 --> 21:53.180
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

21:59.052 --> 22:00.153
NICE WORK, RABBI.

22:00.187 --> 22:02.890
WELL, THANK YOU.
I'VE BEEN AT IT A WHILE.

22:02.923 --> 22:04.258
WHAT DO YOU PRACTICE ON?

22:04.291 --> 22:05.459
GOYIM.

22:05.492 --> 22:08.462
I THINK
IT'S A BARBARIC RITUAL.

22:08.495 --> 22:11.798
WELL, IT REPRESENTS A COVENANT
BETWEEN OUR PEOPLE AND GOD.

22:11.832 --> 22:13.100
IT DECREASES PLEASURE.

22:13.133 --> 22:15.135
PAID FOR MY SUMMER HOUSE.

22:16.537 --> 22:18.639
OH, EXCUSE ME.

22:18.672 --> 22:21.542
OH,
WILL YOU LOOK AT THIS.

22:21.575 --> 22:24.878
A PROFESSIONAL WOMAN,
A DOCTOR NO LESS,

22:24.912 --> 22:27.281
PLAYING
A JUVENILE VIDEO GAME.

22:27.314 --> 22:29.950
IT'S JUST SO IMMATURE...
FOR A DOCTOR.

22:29.983 --> 22:32.553
[ Laughing ] I HAD NO IDEA
THIS GAME WAS SO AWESOME.

22:32.586 --> 22:33.587
SO, CLEARLY,

22:33.620 --> 22:36.557
YOU'RE OPEN TO LOOKING
BEYOND FIRST IMPRESSIONS.

22:36.590 --> 22:37.824
I DIDN'T SAY THAT.

22:37.858 --> 22:39.593
AW, DAMN, I JUST DIED.

22:40.961 --> 22:45.766
YOU ARE HERE
'CAUSE YOU LIKE ME, AREN'T YOU?

22:45.799 --> 22:47.401
I'M HERE
BECAUSE NANCY INVITED ME.

22:47.434 --> 22:50.037
AND I AM FASCINATED BY HOW
THIS IS ALL GONNA PLAY OUT

22:50.070 --> 22:51.772
WITH THE GANGSTER
BABY‐DADDY.

22:51.805 --> 22:53.640
I'M OBSESSED
WITH THE DRAMA.

22:53.674 --> 22:54.675
MM‐HMM.

22:54.708 --> 22:56.109
YOU WERE MEAN.

22:56.143 --> 22:58.111
I WAS HONEST.
THAT'S NOT MEAN.

22:58.145 --> 23:00.480
IT WAS HARSH.
IT WAS A SNAP JUDGMENT.

23:00.514 --> 23:03.183
I'M ALMOST INCLINED
TO NOT ASK YOU OUT AGAIN

23:03.217 --> 23:05.819
JUST TO SHOW YOU HOW WRONG
YOU ARE ABOUT ME.

23:05.853 --> 23:07.621
ALMOST?
ALMOST.

23:07.654 --> 23:09.756
ALMOST.

23:12.526 --> 23:14.261
ALL RIGHT.

23:14.294 --> 23:15.896
WHITEFISH?

23:15.929 --> 23:19.132
DIMES GO IN THE LIPSTICKS.

23:19.166 --> 23:21.835
EIGHTHS GO IN THE COMPACTS.

23:21.869 --> 23:24.905
HALF OUNCES
IN THE EYE‐SHADOW KIT.

23:24.938 --> 23:26.406
THIS IS EXCITING.

23:26.440 --> 23:28.842
WHEN ARE YOU GONNA BREAK
THE NEWS TO DOUG AND SILAS?

23:28.876 --> 23:29.743
[ SIGHS ]

23:29.776 --> 23:31.645
I'M WORKING UP TO THAT.

23:31.678 --> 23:33.180
WELL,
YOU BETTER DO IT SOON

23:33.213 --> 23:35.115
BEFORE THAT SWELLING
GOES DOWN.

23:35.148 --> 23:37.150
YOU FRACTURED MY CHEEKBONE.

23:37.184 --> 23:39.653
THERE'S SOME OLD GYM EQUIPMENT
IN THE GARAGE.

23:39.686 --> 23:40.954
I'VE BEEN LIFTING.

23:40.988 --> 23:42.756
YOU LOOK GOOD.

23:44.758 --> 23:45.759
THANK YOU.

23:54.334 --> 23:55.335
FROM A DRAWER?

23:55.369 --> 23:56.136
THAT'S RIGHT.

23:56.170 --> 23:57.838
CAN YOU FIX IT OR NOT?

23:57.871 --> 23:58.839
GO SEE A DOCTOR.

23:58.872 --> 24:00.340
I DON'T HAVE
ANY INSURANCE.

24:00.374 --> 24:02.442
I'VE BEEN TAPING IT
TO A POPSICLE STICK,

24:02.476 --> 24:03.677
AND IT'S TURNING BLUE.

24:03.710 --> 24:05.979
TRY CHERRY.

24:09.016 --> 24:11.018
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

24:18.625 --> 24:20.394
I DID NOT APPROVE THIS.

24:20.427 --> 24:22.930
NOW HE LOOKS LIKE
HIS DADDY.

24:22.963 --> 24:24.231
YEAH.

24:24.264 --> 24:26.466
AND YOU, TOO, FROM WHAT I HEAR.
BUT SLIGHTLY SMALLER.

24:26.500 --> 24:29.036
MY SON IS NOT JEWISH.

24:29.069 --> 24:30.470
OH, YEAH, HE IS NOW.

24:30.504 --> 24:33.207
IT'S AN ANCIENT
AND SCHOLARLY RELIGION.

24:33.240 --> 24:35.876
DISPROPORTIONATE NUMBERS
OF NOBEL PRIZE WINNERS.

24:35.909 --> 24:37.878
MEET MY SON ‐‐
AVI MELECH.

24:37.911 --> 24:39.780
THAT'S HIS HEBREW NAME.

24:39.813 --> 24:41.582
"AVI" MEANS "MY FATHER."

24:41.615 --> 24:42.983
"MELECH" ‐‐ THE KING.

24:43.016 --> 24:44.151
That's my boy.

24:44.184 --> 24:46.887
IN ENGLISH,
IT'S STEVEN RAY BOTWIN.

24:46.920 --> 24:48.889
STEVIE RAY.

24:48.922 --> 24:50.924
WOULD YOU LIKE A BAGEL
WITH WHITEFISH?

24:50.958 --> 24:53.160
NANCY...

24:53.193 --> 24:56.997
I'M GONNA HAVE TO SPEAK WITH YOU
PRIVATELY.

25:09.243 --> 25:11.812
THIS IS UNACCEPTABLE.

25:11.845 --> 25:14.314
MY SON, OUR SON,

25:14.348 --> 25:17.751
WILL BE BAPTIZED
BY A PRIEST IN A CHURCH.

25:17.784 --> 25:19.786
SORRY, HE'S JEWISH.

25:19.820 --> 25:21.288
SNIP, SNIP.

25:21.321 --> 25:24.358
EAT FISH.
START SAVING FOR LAW SCHOOL.

25:24.391 --> 25:25.425
I AM HIS FATHER.

25:25.459 --> 25:26.426
I CHOOSE HIS LIFE.

25:26.460 --> 25:28.395
YOU HAD YOUR CHANCE
TO CHOOSE.

25:28.428 --> 25:29.263
YOU WALKED OUT.

25:29.296 --> 25:31.098
I HAVE TO THINK
ABOUT THE BABY NOW.

25:31.131 --> 25:32.366
YOU THINK ABOUT YOURSELF.

25:32.399 --> 25:34.334
DON'T PRETEND
THAT'S A MOTHER'S LOVE.

25:34.368 --> 25:36.236
THIS FROM THE MAN
WHO REFUSED TO PUT HIS NAME

25:36.270 --> 25:37.604
ON HIS OWN SON'S
BIRTH CERTIFICATE!

25:37.638 --> 25:40.107
MY SON'S NOT GONNA BE RAISED
BY THAT PENDEJO!

25:40.140 --> 25:42.209
THAT PENDEJO STICKS AROUND.

25:42.242 --> 25:44.745
HE FIGHTS
FOR WHAT HE LOVES.

25:44.778 --> 25:46.480
AND HE'S NOT A COWARD.

25:50.817 --> 25:52.853
GET OUT.
OKAY.

25:52.886 --> 25:54.054
GET OUT.
OKAY.

25:54.087 --> 25:56.123
MY SON WON'T GROW UP
TO BE LIKE YOU.

25:56.156 --> 25:57.958
HE WON'T SEE YOU.

25:57.991 --> 26:00.093
HE WON'T KNOW YOU.

26:02.563 --> 26:05.065
HE IS MINE.

26:05.098 --> 26:06.533
NO, YOU LOST HIM.

26:11.171 --> 26:13.707
[ UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYS ]

26:13.740 --> 26:15.309
[ SIGHS ]

26:22.850 --> 26:24.785
[ DOOR OPENS ]

26:24.818 --> 26:27.221
[ BABY FUSSING ]

26:29.156 --> 26:32.993
[ MAN SINGING IN HEBREW ]

